node.title: Northland drivers told to 'expect delays' after serious crash on State Highway 1
node.description: Waka Kotahi is urging motorists to pass the scene with care.
node.content: ["There has been a serious crash on State Highway 1 in Northland.", "The crash occurred on Thursday afternoon near the beach town of Waipu, near Uretiti Rd, the New Zealand Transport Agency - Waka Kotahi says.", "Waka Kotahi is urging motorists to pass the scene with care and expect delays, and will provide further updates in due course.", "Newshub has contacted police for further information."]
